### 9. Resources (Unified model for Notes/Books/Questions)
# @name createResource
POST {{baseUrl}}/resources
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
    "type": "book",
    "title": "Experience Human Development - 14th Ed.",
    "subtitle": "Diane Papalia",
    "subtitle_type": "Author",
    "course_code": "psy-404",
    "file_url": "https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/...",
